  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">EDUCATION ON HUMAN RIGHTS:BUILDING A CULTURE OF RESPECT FOR DEMOCRACY AND JUSTICE</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project provides technical cooperation to the Brazilian Human Rights Secretariat in the field of human rights education (HRE). UNESCO consultants and actions planned throughout the project implementation have been instrumental to consolidate a culture of human rigths in Brazilian schools, which was ultimately translated into the adoption of a Human Rights Education Plan (Plano Nacional de Educa&#xE7;&#xE3;o em Direitos Humanos) and the recent approval (2013) of the curricula guidelines for human rights education.</narrative>
  </description>
